        <updateDate>2013-11-22T20:57:36Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Provides for appellate review by the Merit Systems Protection Board for employees or applicants for employment who were determined ineligible for a sensitive position if: (1) such position does not require a security clearance or access to classified information, and (2) such determination is otherwise appealable. </p>]]></text>
